author: Screen Junkies
description:
It’s the Honest Trailer for Peacemaker! We watched both seasons so you don’t have to, but you should! It’s a good show if you like grounded, mature themes, like when is it ok to shoot your dad or chainsaw a gorilla? James Gunn and John Cena have a good thing going here, it’s a shame Warner Bros is about to be gutted and sold for parts again… 

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)

Written by: Spencer Gilbert and Lon Harris
Produced by: Spencer Gilbert
Edited by: Kevin Williamsen
